Description:
Spring Football Courses (Ages 3 to 12) – Mini, After School & Weekend Options

Join our Spring Football Courses for boys and girls aged 3 to 12, running throughout the school term! With multiple formats to choose from, there’s something for every schedule and skill level—whether your child is just starting out or already kicking with confidence.

✔ Age-specific formats:

– Mini Courses (Ages 3–5): 1h playful sessions focused on motor skills, ball coordination & fun learning in a safe, nurturing setting.

– After School Courses (Ages 5–10): 1h dynamic weekday training to boost technical skills, teamwork & game understanding.

– Weekend Courses (Ages 3–12): 1h30 sessions combining skill-building, match play & team spirit for all levels.

✔ Led by qualified international & bilingual coaches

✔ Safe & friendly environment with First Aid certified staff

✔ Fun weekly topics & small-sided matches

✔ FREE trial session available!

Flexible locations & times make it easy to fit football into your family's schedule. Book now and let your child experience football fun, fitness, and friendship this spring!

Name: Birthday Party
Short description: Celebrate your child’s special day with a fully organized football birthday party! From just CHF 360 for 12 children, enjoy 2 hours of football games, challenges, and mini-tournaments led by qualified coaches. Hosted at a location of your choice (additional venue rental fees may apply). All equipment provided—fun guaranteed!
Description:
Football Birthday Parties – Celebrate Your Child’s Big Day with Fun, Fitness & Football!

Make your child’s birthday unforgettable with an InterSoccer Football Party, designed for boys and girls aged 3 and up. Whether your child is a football fanatic or just loves active fun with friends, our parties deliver an action-packed celebration full of laughter, games, and team spirit.

✓  Fully customizable experience – Tailored activities, themes, and extras to match your wishes
✓  Flexible locations – Hosted at a location of your choice, indoor or outdoor (additional venue rental fees may apply)
✓  Hassle-free setup – We provide all football equipment, manage the flow, and take care of everything
✓  Fun & inclusive games – Engaging drills, football challenges, and a mini-tournament for all skill levels
✓  Safe & friendly environment – Experienced, bilingual coaches with First Aid certification

Party includes:
– 2 hours of football fun
– Up to 12 children (custom options for more)
– 1 InterSoccer medal & T-shirt for the birthday child
– Equipment provided: balls, bibs, cones, and goals
– Optional extras:  extra medals and t-shirts (additional fees apply)

Make it a birthday to remember—book your child’s football party today!

Girls-Only Summer Football Camps in Geneva (Ages 5 to 13) 

This summer, give your daughter the chance to thrive on and off the field at our Girls-Only Summer Football Camps in Geneva! Designed exclusively for girls aged 5 to 13, these camps combine sport, self-confidence, and community in a supportive and empowering environment.

Spaces are limited – early booking is highly recommended!

Name: InterCommunity School Zurich - One Day Autumn Camp
Short description:
Girls and boys of all abilities from Pre-K to Grade 5 are welcome, however we
strongly advise that children younger than Grade 1 only select a half day.
It is possible to join morning only from 08:30 - 12:00, afternoon only from 12:30 - 16:00,
or full day from 08:30 - 16:00 (Grade 1 to 5). Children can be taken out of camp
anytime for their meetings and brought back to camp.
Please bring your own packed lunch and/or snacks for full day participants.
